keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map J nextTab
map K previousTab
map <c-d> scrollPageDown
map <c-u> scrollPageUp
map <a-e> Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map ;y LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl
map <c-6> visitPreviousTab
map ;; LinkHints.activateMode action=focus
map <c-o> goBack
map <c-i> goForward
searchEngines:
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
gh: https://github.com/search?q=%s Github
ghd: https://github.com/doctolib/?q=%s&type=all&language=&sort= Github Doctolib
t: https://www.linguee.com/english-french/search?source=auto&query=%s Translate
thes: https://www.thesaurus.com/browse/%s Thesaurus
thes2: https://www.freethesaurus.com/%s Thesaurus2
gif: https://duckduckgo.com/?q=%s&t=canonical&atb=v117-6&iar=images&iaf=type%3Agif&iax=images&ia=images Gif
jira: https://doctolib.atlassian.net/secure/QuickSearch.jspa?searchString=P3C-%s Jira
cf: https://doctolib.atlassian.net/wiki/search/?text=%s Confluence
nixp: https://search.nixos.org/packages?channel=unstable&from=0&size=50&sort=relevance&type=packages&query=%s Nix Packages
nixhm: https://mynixos.com/search?q=%s Search HM & NixOS options
hm: https://home-manager-options.extranix.com/?query=%s&release=master Search HM options
